reviewText: Just as advertised!  Great addition to my library!  A must for Ed Wynn fans!
Here is a great DVD! Ed Wynne is an Original. and so is the Camel cigarettes in his adveritsing, really worth it.
Everything was on time and in good condition and I enjoyed watching the show.  He was a funny guy.  I hope you will enjoy too.

If your a Ed Wynn or early TV fan you'll overlook the rather corny vaudville style entertainment and grainy kinescope quality and enjoy this. It's truly peering into what TV was like in those early post-war years. Ed's little ad-libs here and there are the funniest parts! I only wish they left in the great original camel animated commercials.
